# Enkana Fresh — Typography Scale

All text uses the scale below. CSS variables and utility classes are in `client/src/index.css`.

## Font families

- `--font-display`: 'Fraunces', serif — headings, hero, page titles, metric values, brand.
- `--font-sans`: 'DM Sans', sans-serif — body, UI, labels, tables, forms, nav.
- `--font-mono`: system monospace — **only** footer build info and OTP/MFA input.

## Variables (:root)

- **Sizes:** `--text-hero` 42px, `--text-page` 28px, `--text-section` 18px, `--text-metric` 32px, `--text-body-lg` 16px, `--text-body` 14px, `--text-body-sm` 13px, `--text-label` 12px, `--text-xs` 11px.
- **Weights:** `--weight-regular` 400, `--weight-medium` 500, `--weight-semibold` 600, `--weight-bold` 700.
- **Colors:** `--color-text-primary` #111827, `--color-text-heading` #1a3a2a, `--color-text-muted` #6b7280, `--color-text-subtle` #9ca3af, `--color-text-inverse` #ffffff, `--color-text-cream` #f5f0e8, `--color-text-amber` #e9a82a, `--color-text-error` #dc2626, `--color-text-nav` #374151.

