## Page layout (compact)

- Content wrapper: `p-4 max-w-5xl mx-auto min-h-full bg-background`.
- Section spacing: `mb-3` / `mb-4`; card padding: `p-3`.

## Do not

- Use `font-family: Georgia`, `serif`, or `system-ui` — use `var(--font-display)` or `var(--font-sans)`.
- Use monospace except for footer and OTP/MFA fields.
- Use hardcoded font sizes outside the scale; use the variables or utility classes above.
